summary: Adds a new made from scratch dungeon with no copy and paste. Lore friendly
descriptionHtml:
A mediem sized HIGH player level dungeon south west of Stendarr\'s Beacon. Uses a dwemer ruin map marker in case you cant find it.
Has a few secrets and powerful enemies, and a treasure room at the end.
In the treasure room there is levelled treasure plus an item containing a new enchantment that will prove useful for some adventurers.

Install by copying esp to skyrim/data

You may not use this in another mod, upload anywhere else (including steam workshop) etc etc.
If you wish to use it, ask me first and I may say yes if its a large mod that combines many dungeon mods for example.
author: thelonewarrior
